.SH "EXAMPLES"
Examples of both success and failure from a private and public key:
.
.IP "" 4
.
.nf

$ jose jwk gen \-i \'{"alg":"ES256"}\' \-o prv\.jwk
$ jose jwk pub \-i prv\.jwk \-o pub\.jwk
$ jose jwk use \-i prv\.jwk \-u sign
$ echo $?
0
$ jose jwk use \-i pub\.jwk \-u sign
$ echo $?
1
.
.fi
